{"tid":2294250,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[試食有圖] 佐敦黃店泰菜(內無精液太陽蛋)","createTime":"2020-11-21T01:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T19:07:34.000Z","uid":182895,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a18225ef68875c0837ab9ee446764b20716fe035","tid":2294250,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:24:14.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">(好啦我唔再講大渣哥隻神級透明精液太陽蛋了)</span><br />\n<br />\n勁鐘意食泰菜, 都有唔少黃店選擇, 今次試呢間<br />\n <br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">泰灜</span></span><br />\n佐敦吳松街141號地舖<br />\n <br />\nSummary:<br />\n1) 店內有黃店裝飾, 同現場睇檔嘅吹左幾句, 無問題<br />\n2) 環境可以, 小店唔好要求咁多, 廁所乾淨<br />\n3) 食物整體幾好, 唔算非常泰國風味(絕大部份香港泰菜都唔係), 但有心做好食物<br />\n4) 價錢好合理, 可再J<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n圖<br />\n <br />\n小食併<br />\n炸野唔錯, 交貨野但香口, 生菜包出色, 雞翼無特別<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTATunc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTATunc.png&h=66b3432c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n燒牛肉<br />\n個汁幾好, 牛無過熟, 有肉味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LktRf2w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLktRf2w.png&h=d7606563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n蠔蛋<br />\n蛋味夠蠔味鮮, 無變成炸蛋<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mMvTunG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmMvTunG.png&h=4d2ce7cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n燒魚<br />\n可以落多d香茅蔥薑係個肚到, 肉剛熟但味唔夠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6oJBr9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6oJBr9s.png&h=5435f64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n魚餅<br />\n調味幾好, 香料十足<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BznuM9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBznuM9A.png&h=4aa8ec75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n串燒<br />\n無過鹹, Juicy無過火, 肉質好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cd6LkuG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCd6LkuG.png&h=4c9c7401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\nPad thai<br />\n中上, 份量足有鑊氣<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPKH69U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPKH69U.png&h=a8804c05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n完"},{"pid":"0546bc5b6624025cc17654a857ee0eb1d5b45a4e","tid":2294250,"uid":35342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:31:34.000Z","msg":"有冇泰式精液辣醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bddfb1b82d10a3040fc4d0cd87ca4ae385909c","tid":2294250,"uid":94490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我入黎啦"},{"pid":"bc411c5a24d798d4bea25bcd7859ffb737158b36","tid":2294250,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75bddfb1b82d10a3040fc4d0cd87ca4ae385909c","tid":2294250,"uid":94490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我入黎啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:47:04.000Z","msg":"Ching 好早喎都<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1612da5ac866d47f9d6ae7c1a307fa5843bf9052","tid":2294250,"uid":199074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:49:58.000Z","msg":"我入黎就係想睇精液太陽蛋圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ea12706d57a0f34792f1cffc30c9b45a5f8a25","tid":2294250,"uid":19962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/